    <tags />
    <narrativeNotes>F was a test subject used by the Empire for their unique genetic potential. Instead of gaining blatant powers with military applications, F developed the apex of biological flexibility, and used their new power to absorb genetic information from others deemed worthy of integrating. Eventually F's psychic potential grew too large from the abundance of genetic alteration, and F fell into the backrooms. There F abanoned any remaining morality and became a leader to other trapped refugees, using them as experiments under the guise of sanctity.</narrativeNotes>
